node.text: We have a race today, but let’s not forget that the marshals are the real heroes of our sport. We wouldn’t be able to do what we do without them 🧡 #RIP

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Lando Norris in Hungaroring. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: 6th and so close to 4th. Shame we missed out but will go for it tomorrow.

node.text: You fans are crazy!! Insane feeling and best part of the day!! And I got P4… thanks everyone for coming, ❤️ you crazy people 🔊

node.text: That was one of the best drives into the track I’ve ever had. Great to see so many of you here. Let’s make it a good one 👊

node.text: P5 and a debrief from @vikkstagram. I’d call that a good day.
